{"tid":967071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"司徒華：香港回歸母體中國是必然的事實，收不回就失去民族自尊。","createTime":"2019-01-03T08:54:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T05:06:44.000Z","uid":49388,"like":2,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d82ef1749472d3fef25b6faff46f7534fae669bd","tid":967071,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:54:25.000Z","msg":"1989年9月1日，六四過去3個月後，香港電台節目「新聞天地」專訪司徒華：<br />\n<br />\n記者：「你指出中國過去幾十年出現很多問題，但在中英會談時，你很早便支持中國收回香港的主權，為什麼呢？」<br />\n<br />\n司徒華：「香港本來就是中國的地方，回歸母體是必然的事實。雖然當時的政權很多地方我並不同意，但假如一個國家對屬於自己的土地也不收回，沒有民族自尊，這個國家和政權是要不得的。我們作為中國人，回歸祖國與十一億人民同命運是很應該的。過去百多年來，我們好像很『僥倖』與中華民族的苦難脫離，但亦有點自咎。所以不論前景如何，我還是支持收回主權，『六‧四』事件並沒有改變我的看法。」<br />\n<br />\nFrom 堂主"},{"pid":"6451e998cac2421062613bbd100ce5b8c6d78b3b","tid":967071,"uid":35430,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T09:01:28.000Z","msg":"過去百多年來，我們好像很『僥倖』與中華民族的苦難脫離，但亦有點自咎。<br />\n<br />\n自乜撚野咎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係華人賤種基因作嘅孽，自作賤關人咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ccfce54307ddf8a15761da677180facc0317852","tid":967071,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T09:07:16.000Z","msg":"0:40<br />\n「為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中國</span></span>同埋民主既路&hellip;<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">香港既民主</span>」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=pGSqLx9Ce34\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpGSqLx9Ce34&d=0uxXn7C%2FpHl%2FswxxB4gUX3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=ca540ab4\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=pGSqLx9Ce34</a>"},{"pid":"6f00443174dfa5e86d7a3966c8684603921357d1","tid":967071,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T09:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e297a1c9086659eb5375b0121728d5df9a0230","tid":967071,"uid"